  <div id="text-content_EAA2B650-010D-0135-F9F2-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To send a chat message, enter your message in the chat window [1]. Then click the <strong>Send </strong>button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

